comments: Nance Jr. (NOP) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Paul (PHX) engages with Jones (NOP) and releases before receiving the pass.

Jones (NOP) attempts to move alongside of Paul's (PHX) path to the basket but Paul stops and steps into Jones' path.  The contact is marginal and Paul does not unnaturally veer into Jones or otherwise dislodge him from his position.
Nance Jr. (NOP) swipes down and makes contact with Bridges' (PHX) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Ingram (NOP) briefly grasps Johnson's (PHX) arm extended into his path, but quickly releases and the contact is marginal.
Crowder (PHX) commits a take foul on McCollum (NOP).
Paul (PHX) places his arm against Jones (NOP) and the contact is marginal as he stops and changes directions during the throw-in.
Paul (PHX) slows down in Jones' (NOP) path and Jones continues forward into him, but the contact is marginal.
Nance Jr. (NOP) reaches in and makes contact to Paul's (PHX) arm that affects his SQBR.  The foul occurs at the 00:36.9 mark, and the game clock is reset after it continues to run after the whistle.
Craig (PHX) moves forward and initiates contact with Ingram's (NOP) lower body that affects his jump shot attempt.
Jones (NOP) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).
McCollum (NOP) places his off-arm against Johnson (PHX), who begins to fall to the floor in an attempt to draw the foul.  Johnson is not dislodged from his position by the contact from McCollum.
Murphy III (NOP) commits a take foul on Bridges (PHX).
Johnson (PHX) and McCollum (NOP) engage in marginal arm contact that does not affect McCollum's driving shot attempt.
Ingram (NOP) commits a take foul on Bridges (PHX).
Craig (PHX) and Murphy III (NOP) mutually engage during the inbound and the contact is marginal.
Nance Jr. (NOP) dislodges Johnson (PHX) from his position during the rebound.
